00:46:51.160 --> 00:46:53.624
I thought, people
are doing this work.

00:46:53.624 --> 00:46:54.790
They're teaching this stuff.

00:46:54.790 --> 00:46:55.840
They're advising the government.

00:46:55.840 --> 00:46:56.840
They're running the government.

00:46:56.840 --> 00:46:58.673
They're writing these
papers, this and that.

00:46:58.673 --> 00:47:01.230
They have terrible data.

00:47:01.230 --> 00:47:02.670
They have really
stupid analysis.

00:47:02.670 --> 00:47:05.030
And the biggest thing, the
