00:47:09.780 --> 00:47:12.570
Every single one of them,
if they were buying a car,

00:47:12.570 --> 00:47:15.320
they would spend a lot more
serious commonsense analysis

00:47:15.320 --> 00:47:17.790
to get the right car
than they do recommending

00:47:17.790 --> 00:47:21.260
a plan for the government to
