00:47:21.260 --> 00:47:24.240
or something like that.

00:47:24.240 --> 00:47:27.360
And a lot of other
people felt the same way.

00:47:27.360 --> 00:47:29.260
And we had both
some philosophical

00:47:29.260 --> 00:47:33.280
and some empirical
ideas that we were

00:47:33.280 --> 00:47:36.050
sold on the idea of
quantitative analysis.

00:47:36.050 --> 00:47:38.962
We were confident in our
