00:48:03.050 --> 00:48:07.740
If you won't, you're just
an idiot loser chattering.

00:48:07.740 --> 00:48:10.105
You'd start really thinking
about things if you actually

00:48:10.105 --> 00:48:13.900
have to bet money on
anything, any opinion you get.

00:48:13.900 --> 00:48:16.000
A lot of silly
chattering conversation

00:48:16.000 --> 00:48:21.230
