00:48:24.584 --> 00:48:25.750
OK, I want to go to a place.

00:48:25.750 --> 00:48:28.654
I want to prove that
my methods work.

00:48:28.654 --> 00:48:30.570
And the way I'm going
to prove my methods work

00:48:30.570 --> 00:48:32.611
is I'm going to go to
places where people gamble,

00:48:32.611 --> 00:48:34.742
and I'm going to
